: ""}, {"cid": 2997931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 567920, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人家单亲家庭，母亲卖房给儿子留学的，这都能被仇富的喷😅", "timestamp": 1637468801, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997932, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 567920, "reply_to": 2997911, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 分配不合理→贫富差距→社会撕裂→不同阶层间共情能力降低→矛盾升高→社会思潮极端化", "timestamp": 1637468812, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997950, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 567920, "reply_to": 2997911, "tag": null, "text": "爱国主义和国族主义构建一定程度上可以缓解这种矛盾，当然矛盾激化到一定程度时，再猛的爱国主义和国族主义宣传都趋于无效。", "timestamp": 1637468912, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997979, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 567920, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "反正凡事皆可仇富，只要你不是捡垃圾睡大街衣不蔽体，都能被喷", "timestamp": 1637469181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2998155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 567920, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然我同情惋惜这位留学生，也准备留学，虽然我知道这篇回答的论据和逻辑都有问题，但我觉得这种仇富是好事", "timestamp": 1637471084, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 567920, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/499577138/answer/2233892114\n如何看待", "timestamp": 1637468262, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637471085, "url": "", "vote": {}}}